<p>Resolve to Save Lives is housed within Vital Strategies, a global health organization that works in 60 countries to address the world’s most challenging health issues. Resolve to Save Lives fits perfectly with Vital Strategies’ vision of a world where every person is protected by a strong public health system.</p>